{"type": "article", "id": 13894, "title": "Tom Ford 口红手拿包", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-24T08:03:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000246alQ8tks65uZMcv49.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tTom Ford 最近推出了一款非常贴心的手拿包，他们在里面做了一个专门放置口红或唇膏的小暗格，解决了晚会中常常遇到的手忙脚乱翻口红的问题，同时，里面还有拉链小袋子和卡片格子，分工非常明确到位。除了“务实”的里子，它外观上却是金光闪闪，看上去蛮高调。这是<a href=\"http://www.net-a-porter.com/Shop/Designers/Tom_Ford/Bags?pn=1&amp;npp=60&amp;image_view=product&amp;dScroll=0&amp;cm_mmc=LinkshareUS-_-JlFzVGPAZUQ-_-Custom-_-LinkBuilder&amp;siteID=JlFzVGPAZUQ-CEolHi6lW.uu9z_9UXCIsQ\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141542kjd9P1L3FnKzuTqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141542eNZVowa2LrP08S1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}